        <gi>linkingObjectIdentifier</gi>
    </head>
    <div type="semanticcomponents">
        <!-- PREMIS Semantic components -->
        <p>linkingObjectIdentifierType</p>
        <p>linkingObjectIdentifierValue</p>
        <p>linkingObjectRole</p>
    </div>
    <div type="definition">
        <!-- PREMIS Definition -->
        <p>The identifier of an object associated with the Rights statement.</p>
    </div>
    <div type="rationale">
        <!-- PREMIS Rationale -->
        <p>Rights statements must be associated with the objects to which they
            pertain, either by linking from the Rights statement to the object(s) or
            by linking from the object(s) to the Rights statement. This semantic
            unit provides the mechanism for the link from the Rights statement to an
            object.</p>
    </div>
